        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Last updated: <span id="pp-date">2025-01-01</span></p>
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>YT2MP3 provides a tool to convert publicly accessible YouTube videos to MP3. We are committed to protecting your privacy and minimizing the data we process.</p>
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <ul class="steps">
          <li>Technical data: standard web server logs (IP address, user-agent, timestamp) to operate and secure the service.</li>
          <li>Request data: the YouTube URL you submit to perform the conversion.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>What We Do Not Collect</h2>
        <ul class="steps">
          <li>We do not require account registration.</li>
          <li>We do not store converted files permanently. Links returned by third-party providers may expire.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Use of Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information solely to provide and improve the conversion service, prevent abuse, troubleshoot, and maintain security.</p>
        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We may use third-party APIs to process conversions. These providers may receive your submitted video ID/URL as part of the request. Refer to their policies for more details.</p>
        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>We do not use tracking cookies. A local preference may be stored in your browser for theme selection.</p>
        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <p>Server logs are retained for a limited period necessary for security and operational reasons and then deleted or anonymized.</p>
        <h2>Security</h2>
        <p>We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect the service; however, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.</p>
        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct, or delete personal data. Contact us to submit a request.</p>
        <h2>Children’s Privacy</h2>
        <p>YT2MP3 is not directed to children under 13. If you believe a child has provided personal data, contact us to remove it.</p>
        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Material changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:chavezdave.a@gmail.com">chavezdave.a@gmail.com</a></p>
